[[!tag Energy_Drink Review]]

Tribute Active Mandarin Live Wild Lime is one of the more widely available Rip
Its, at least at the stores near me. I know all 3 places I can get Rip Its
within a 3 mile radius of me (an [[Exxon]], Citgo and the Dollar Tree) and 2 of
those locations routinely have this flavor.

